  characterName: Kishida Mie
  description: She's a bit of a pervert and while she likes to act aloof on her own,
    she's quite perceptive, leading her to be rather antisocial. Drawn in by her
    passion for (adult) books, Takasu Mitsuko would approach her with the intention
    of becoming friends, regardless of how many times she would get turned down.
    Through their bond, they learn to become more open about themselves.
